With line numbers
docs.text:
def bubble_sort(arr):  
    for n in range(len(arr) - 1, 0, -1):
        swapped = False  
        for i in range(n):
            if arr[i] > arr[i + 1]:
                arr[i], arr[i + 1] = arr[i + 1], arr[i]
                swapped = True
        if not swapped:
            break

def bubble_sort(arr):  
    for n in range(len(arr) - 1, 0, -1):
        swapped = False  
        for i in range(n):
            if arr[i] > arr[i + 1]:
                arr[i], arr[i + 1] = arr[i + 1], arr[i]
                swapped = True
        if not swapped:
            break
